high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter then take a small step to your right.
Pick up the potato that's in front of you. to the left of the frying pan.
Turn right and walk to the sink on your left then turn left to face it.
Wash the potato in the sink and then take it back out and close the tap.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.

high_descs: turn around and move to the counter where the spatula is sitting
pick up the potato off of the counter
turn to the right, move forward to the sink that is on the left hand side, turn to face the sink
put the potato in to the sink, turn on the water to wash off the potato, turn off the water and remove the potato from the sink
turn to the left and move to the microwave
open the microwave door, put the potato inside and close the door
anns.task_desc: put a clean potato in to the microwave

high_descs: Walk to the counter on your left.
Grab a potato from the counter.

Wash the potato in the sink and grab it.
Walk to the microwave on your left.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Wash a potato and heat it.
